{"tid":2293088,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[行山撚] 上花坑即興遊","createTime":"2020-11-20T04:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T04:12:49.000Z","uid":121784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3c14db35caf6be40523d61f72d6ded00560972","tid":2293088,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"某日早收工, 離天黑仲有個零兩個鐘, 於是即興去附近山頭尋幽探秘<br />\n上花坑網上可以搵到既資料極少, 相信無乜行山隊行過<br />\n<a href=\"http://600-hk-streams.blogspot.com/2015/01/blog-post_25.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F600-hk-streams.blogspot.com%2F2015%2F01%2Fblog-post_25.html&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BUKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=a62c2232\" target=\"_blank\">http://600-hk-streams.blogspot.com/2015/01/blog-post_25.html</a><br />\n<br />\n坐39M去到荃威花園總站落車, 經荃威花園上引水道, 係呢度左轉烈女宮, 靠右上山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oy9dnee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foy9dnee.jpg&h=9aca4eb3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過橋後, 係分叉路跟絲帶靠左繼續上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wiQ8UG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wiQ8UG.jpg&h=ad5f987a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 去到第二條引水道, 轉左前行少少, 係水池右邊小徑入澗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Comv8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Comv8b.jpg&h=22b7d131&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n回望入澗位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/du6Wj2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdu6Wj2e.jpg&h=938cf20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條澗入口睇上去好陰森, 青苔好勁, 但行落又幾暢通喎. 仲有石間小瀑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7jkMHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7jkMHH.jpg&h=83421b04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4c35XPp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4c35XPp.jpg&h=1ab6dc17&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為就快天黑關係, 無時間繼續上溯, 於是係240米左右既分源位, 轉上右源, 希望天黑前爆到出大路.<br />\n右源完全搵唔到記載, 一般地圖都無標示呢條分源, 只有憑地政總署既地圖(係山上信號差, 廢左一半武功)同埋方向感向前<br />\n<br />\n右源比起主源密唔少, 但小心D有刺植物, 捐下爬下又過到, 唔駛爆林<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KU8NrJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKU8NrJQ.jpg&h=f90da1d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n急升左一陣, 爬埋呢個小瀑, 到270米左右, 睇GPS已經好接近山徑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8XuE45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8XuE45.jpg&h=156985d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到廢田既地基, 於是開電筒搵路, 最後係疏少少既地方穿左大約十米林出去康莊大道<br />\n<br />\n落返第二引水道附近既報德亭, 天已幾乎全黑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQT9E6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQT9E6J.jpg&h=2ef7b0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就開電筒, 原路行返落山, 好彩經過村屋時, 一隻村狗都無遇到, 經烈女宮去返第一條引水道, 安全脫險~"}]}